  "contentHtml": "<p>1.&nbsp; <a href=\"https://x.com/ATabarrok/status/2056399339174469827\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">AI-written story published in Granta, wins major literary prize</a>.</p>\n<p>2. <a href=\"https://x.com/jesusferna7026/status/2056341632253862099?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JFV on smart phones as accelerators of fertility declines</a>.</p>\n<p>3. <a href=\"https://www.axios.com/local/washington-dc/2026/05/18/human-composting-earth-funeral-maryland-dc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Maryland markets in everything</a>.</p>\n<p>4. <a href=\"https://x.com/bigmeaninternet/status/2056172207462887776?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Polling Chinese on a top one hundred books</a>.</p>\n<p>5. From the excellent Samir Varma, <a href=\"https://samirvarma.substack.com/p/you-cant-quietly-park-at-01c?r=hfb1h&amp;utm_medium=ios&amp;triedRedirect=true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">could alien drone probes decelerate in time?</a>&nbsp; And here is <a href=\"https://chatgpt.com/share/6a0b7bad-40d4-83ea-b621-4d3035985c19\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">analysis from GPT</a>.</p>\n<p>6. “<span>I am thrilled to announce the launch of </span><a href=\"https://nam11.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=http%3A%2F%2Ftotei.com%2F&amp;data=05%7C02%7Ctcowen%40gmu.edu%7C20e1b238b8a445138a1308deb4d3fafd%7C9e857255df574c47a0c00546460380cb%7C0%7C0%7C639147020195823272%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C80000%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=oeIWibtqDcUMmjU9RpBvgMvYcXeg7NSZdBXHVUhQd9c%3D&amp;reserved=0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Totei.com</a>. Totei is a magazine devoted to craft and craftsmanship in all its forms. The name Totei comes from the ancient Japanese word for apprentice.”&nbsp; From <a href=\"https://conversationswithtyler.com/episodes/gaurav-kapadia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gaurav Kapadia</a>.</p>\n<p>7. <a href=\"https://www.semafor.com/article/05/18/2026/ai-skepticism-grows-among-us-youth\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">The young seem to like AI the least</a>.</p>\n<p>8. <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/18/business/economy/edmund-phelps-dead.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">NYT obituary for Edmund Phelps</a>.</p>",
